WEBVTT

00:00:59.360 --> 00:01:02.696
You choose not to tell anyone
for fear of losing your job

00:01:02.720 --> 00:01:04.400
or being seen as weak.

00:01:06.080 --> 00:01:07.976
You give the vision a name,

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:10.096
Bloody Face in Bunker,

00:01:10.120 --> 00:01:12.440
and call it BFIB for short.

00:01:13.800 --> 00:01:17.016
You keep BFIB locked away in your mind,

00:01:17.040 --> 00:01:18.816
secretly haunting you,

00:01:18.840 --> 00:01:22.160
for the next seven years.

00:01:23.680 --> 00:01:25.280
Now close your eyes.

00:01:27.160 --> 00:01:28.520
Can you see BFIB?